<p><b>Firefighting</b> is the act of extinguishing <a href="Fire" title="Fire">fires</a>. A <a href="Firefighter" title="Firefighter">firefighter</a> fights fires to prevent loss of life, and/or destruction of property and the environment. Firefighting is a highly technical skill that requires professionals who have spent years training in both general firefighting techniques and specialized areas of expertise.</p>
